Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把日和的記憶{\rsymbol}…{\r}還給她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堵住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 從裡面捅不破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗神如今仍未回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎麼還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了趕快逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神是什麼 還有那不再冷酷的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾所認識的那個禍津神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禍津神夜斗在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雙飽含執念的美麗眸子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個夜斗神在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾望得一戰的是那個禍津神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 蠃蚌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大規模的時化{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要生亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖們全都不安份起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兆麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小福閣下說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時化不是風穴所致吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是荒亂的禍津神催生之物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禍津神?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帶上日和 離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠃蚌本就是衝我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去吸引他的注意力 你們趁機逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那夜斗怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了我豈不是手無寸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 我會想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是封印著日和記憶的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:07:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往事若夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 日和{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗 怎麼辦啊夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和不睜眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管她 夜斗神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已是無聲無心的空容器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一堆肉塊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠃蚌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恨吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒御魂啊 憎恨吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勿要抗拒恨意之渦 覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禍津神夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是那雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張笑臉 我要切得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這天空與吾等生存的時代相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾等乃是禍津神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回應不淨之願 以血染遍此岸的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠃蚌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 吾一直在等此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻正是成就吾願之時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾名為蠃蚌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握己名諱存於意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獻吾之軀為汝依
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匯聚而來眾多之名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速聽吾命不可違抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勿要聽他人調遣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匯聚吧 丑氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在{\rsymbol}…{\r}吸收時化?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活太久傻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和妖同化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非也 夜斗神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為與原本的你 盡情一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗 喂 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都{\rsymbol}…{\r}不懂{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個香氣是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠃蚌過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪裡聞過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 喜歡的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日{\rsymbol}…{\r}日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什什什什{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叢林{\rsymbol}…{\r}迴旋踢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己解開了我的術?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記憶的封蓋竟然會解開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要臉 你在做什麼啊 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才叫我{\rsymbol}…{\r}夜斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和的記憶 回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 我{\rsymbol}…{\r}為什麼{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何不變回往日的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾等乃是禍津神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受不淨之願 以人的慾望與憎恨為食糧{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少把那些不能當飯吃的往日舊事掛在嘴邊沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開日和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,區區半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿你做吾力量之祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要斬咯 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 從這裡會傷到日和{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和境界一個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠃蚌現在吸收了時化 與妖同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斬斷什麼 放過什麼 好好分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豐葦原之中津國中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒亂無度的彼岸之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾 夜斗神顯聖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此雪器斬碎降服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將業障重重之穢跡{\rsymbol}…{\r}盡數祓除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點回去吧 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜{\rsymbol}…{\r}夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗{\rsymbol}…{\r}神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的臉{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是用詛咒強行保持著身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論多少次實現他們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們對禍津神仍是懼怕 厭惡 遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論善惡 人心總難恆一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此乃真理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被忘卻所殺乃吾等命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 從五百年沉睡中甦醒之時 吾發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其殞身不識吾者之手 不如讓汝這知吾之人動手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先行一步了 夜斗神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與吾擁有同樣命運的神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個神明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉 失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要回去告訴父親才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的都想起來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括我的事和夜斗的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼記憶突然回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為夜斗的{\rsymbol}…{\r}香{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢 我不記得啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然又正經起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我們斷緣比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你更能過得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想斬斷和你們之間的緣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和親說了那種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又是莫名其妙瞎逞強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今後也想一直和你們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻突然說什麼要斷緣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀啊 日和親好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒 擺喜酒
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}喜酒\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 想在一起不是那種奇怪的意思{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個願望我幫你實現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五日元
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一岐日和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fscx500\bord1.5}\h{\fscx100}五元\N{\r}願你我不無緣份
