Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:27.48,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その手を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:33.04,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}連れてくから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.15,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}言えないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:44.35,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}この手を強く握って
